	<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/simonandru/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/935cc5e7bf09e11bf9895480b1faf0a0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/935cc5e7bf09e11bf9895480b1faf0a0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/simonandru/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">simonandru</a> <span class=\"review-date\">април 5, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">User-friendly UI and does what it says</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ifprint/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cef48fe086461290e5c84146fb02455c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cef48fe086461290e5c84146fb02455c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ifprint/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ifprint</a> <span class=\"review-date\">април 2, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Despite encountering issues during the plugin setup, their proactive approach in reaching out to understand the problem and working towards a resolution showcases excellent <strong>customer service</strong>. Kudos to them for their dedication! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pmorais/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c811b6320a4c095b6a890feb96ed9515?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c811b6320a4c095b6a890feb96ed9515?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pmorais/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pmorais</a> <span class=\"review-date\">март 29, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It has some problems managing many images but otherwise it works very well. Support is also fast and efficient.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:139:\"Automatically compress, optimize and serve scaled images as well as convert WebP &amp; AVIF all from CloudFront CDN. Lazy load included ⚡\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:5:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=3019688\";s:7:\"caption\";s:11:\"Connect API\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=3015969\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"General Settings\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=3015969\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Advance Settings\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-4.gif?rev=3019688\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Cloud Library\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-5.gif?rev=3019688\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Cloud Storage\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:101:{s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin