(168, 1, '2024-05-31 12:14:41', '2024-05-31 10:14:41', '{\n    \"hestia::hestia_contact_content_new\": {\n        \"value\": \"[caption id=\\\"attachment_121\\\" align=\\\"aligncenter\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\"]<img src=\\\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/japage1-min-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\" height=\\\"666\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-121 size-full\\\" /> Smje\\u0161tene na samom zapadnom dijelu kupre\\u0161kog polja. Zapravo se radi o pet vrta\\u010da koje su raspore\\u0111ene na povr\\u0161ini od otprilike 1 km2, a u okviru te povr\\u0161ine se nalazi i jedno jezero. Najve\\u0107e od njih je Kotli\\u0107. Put koji vodi do njih je sporedni put kojim se vozite nakon magistralne ceste Kupres \\u2013 \\u0160ipovo. Udaljeni su svega 12km od centra grada zapadno prema gradu \\u0160ipovo. Vjerujemo kako \\u0107e i vas ove vrta\\u010de ostaviti bez daha.[/caption]\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2024-05-31 10:14:41\"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4228983e-f743-4311-a67a-db923b0453d0', '', '', '2024-05-31 12:14:41', '2024-05-31 10:14:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=168', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
